==English==
===Verb===
'''deeky'''
# (''[[Geordie]]'') to [[look]], alternative form of [[deek]].

===Usage Notes===
English [[Geordie]] [[slang]] that means 'look at'.
For example, if one person was to tell another to look at a [[worm]] they would say, ''"Deeky that worm"''.

===Related Terms===
* (''[[Geordie]]'') [[deek]]
* (''[[Geordie]]'') [[deeksies]]
* (''Standard English'') [[look]]

